    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People employed by a national government or ruler to conduct official negotiations and maintain political, economic, and social relations with other nations or international organizations.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
